Invocation Name: my bicycle facts
des: From the 1800s through World War 2 to the present day, from China to America and Amsterdam, here are some interesting facts about bicycles! Bicycles are one of the most efficient modes of transportation, and millions of bicycles are made each year. But did you know how many bicycles are recovered from the canals of Amsterdam each year? Or the fastest speed record for a person riding a bicycle?
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
